OL,3,C'I was struggling to breathe': Fire
OL,4,Cbrigade's warning over cleaning
OL,5,Cproducts
OL,7,FLondoners are being warned of the
OL,8,Fdangers of mixing common cleaning
OL,9,Fproducts together after callouts to
OL,10,Fchemical incidents.
OL,12,FLondon Fire Brigade (LFB) says
OL,13,Faccidentally combining products can
OL,14,Ftrigger a chemical reaction and
OL,15,Funleash dangerous fumes.
OL,17,FSince 2023, the Brigade has attended
OL,18,Fmore than 150 incidents involving
OL,19,Fcleaning chemicals which have
OL,20,Ftriggered a dangerous reaction.
