OL,3,C'I was struggling to breathe': Fire
OL,4,Cbrigade's warning over cleaning
OL,5,Cproducts
OL,7,FChemical incidents require specially
OL,8,Ftrained and equipped officers to
OL,9,Fidentify and deal with these dangerous
OL,10,Fcombinations.
OL,12,FOne man in Plumstead, south east
OL,13,FLondon, who ended up in hospital says
OL,14,Fhe won't mix chemicals again after
OL,15,Fmixing two common cleaning products.
OL,17,FSantosh Karma was exposed to dangerous
OL,18,Fgases after using bleach in his wash
OL,19,Fbasin, toilet, and bath followed by a
OL,20,Fdrain cleaner.
