OL,3,C'I was struggling to breathe': Fire
OL,4,Cbrigade's warning over cleaning
OL,5,Cproducts
OL,7,FDescribing the incident the IT worker
OL,8,Fsaid: "The mixture started to produce
OL,9,Fgases, and as I continued cleaning I
OL,10,Fbegan to have trouble breathing and
OL,11,Fstarted coughing.
OL,13,F"I opened the small bathroom window,
OL,14,Fbut it didn't help. I knew something
OL,15,Fwasn't right, so I rushed out of the
OL,16,Fbathroom.
OL,18,F"After a few minutes I was struggling
OL,19,Fto breathe.
